  <name>SimpleShot</name>
  <summary>Simple screen capture and recording tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      SimpleShot is a lightweight and easy-to-use screen capture and recording application.
      It allows you to quickly capture screenshots or record screen videos with a simple interface.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Area selection with mouse drag</li>
      <li>Screenshot capture with automatic clipboard copy</li>
      <li>Screen recording with visual feedback</li>
      <li>Configurable save locations for images and videos</li>
      <li>Simple and intuitive interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
